structures exhibit a new type of degeneracy in which an infinite number of\neigenvalues asymptotically coalesce. This high degeneracy results in a variety\nof optical phenomena such as strong scattering and enhancement of absorption\nand emission from an atom or molecule by orders of magnitude compared with a\nstandard resonance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jan 2019 23:11:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2019 20:56:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 18 Oct 2019 06:31:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 23 Oct 2019 23:11:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-01"}
