 of underlying PDEs, but are also comparably more accurate than the\nstandard, non-invariant base numerical schemes considered here.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2019 03:43:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
