 thermalization, i.e., the evolution of\nthe disc velocity dispersion profile and its connection with disc\nresponsiveness to manifold spirals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2019 11:52:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-23"}
