e conductance\nor vertex expansion of the community trust graph sufficiently high, a community\nmay grow safely, indefinitely.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2019 14:14:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Jan 2019 08:54:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 20 Jan 2019 16:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 21 May 2020 10:53:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-01"}
