wed remarkable entrapped water beads inside the droplet\nin the form of one or more cavities along the internal layer of the head groups\nwhich was surrounded by lipid head groups. It was also reported that in the\nbuilding structure of the nanoemulsion and SLN, in the central parts of the\ndroplets, lipids were denser than the case of NLCs. Our results indicated that,\nin the case of NLC simulations, the lipid distribution within the lipid matrix\nwas insensitive to the mass fraction of solid to liquid lipids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2019 15:11:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-12"}
